---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Restaurant Marketing in Markham | Toronto Restaurant Growth"
  description="Markham restaurant marketing for the GTA's most vibrant East Asian food hub. First Markham Place, Pacific Mall corridor, and beyond — we help Markham restaurants rank on Google."
>

  <main style="padding-top: 80px;">

    <nav style="padding: 16px 24px; background: #f5f5f0; font-size: 0.85rem;" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/" style="color: #E85D04; text-decoration: none;">Home</a>
      <span style="color: #666; margin: 0 8px;">›</span>
      <a href="/locations/" style="color: #E85D04; text-decoration: none;">Locations</a>
      <span style="color: #666; margin: 0 8px;">›</span>
      Restaurant Marketing Markham
    </nav>

    <section style="background: #1a1a1a; color: #fff; padding: 100px 24px 80px; text-align: center;">
      <div style="max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <p style="text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; font-size: 0.78rem; color: #E85D04; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;">Markham, Ontario</p>
        <h1 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 4rem); color: #fff; margin-bottom: 20px;">Restaurant Marketing in Markham</h1>
        <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: #ccc; max-width: 620px; margin: 0 auto 36px;">
          Markham is home to one of Canada's largest Chinese-Canadian communities and one of the most food-sophisticated dining markets in the GTA. The competition is intense. The customers are discerning. And the search volume is massive.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact/" style="display: inline-block; background: #E85D04; color: #fff; padding: 16px 36px; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem;">Book a Free Google Audit</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section style="background: #fff; padding: 72px 24px;">
      <div style="max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <p style="text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; font-size: 0.78rem; color: #E85D04; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;">The Local Food Scene</p>
        <h2 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem); margin-bottom: 20px;">Markham: The GTA's East Asian Dining Capital</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: #333;">
          If you know where to eat in Markham, you have access to some of the finest Cantonese, Shanghainese, Sichuan, Taiwanese, Hong Kong-style, and Japanese food outside of Asia. The First Markham Place and Pacific Mall corridor has a restaurant density and culinary quality that draws food-obsessed visitors from across the GTA — and beyond.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: #333;">
          Markham's Chinese-Canadian community has a dining culture that's both sophisticated and community-driven. Word-of-mouth through WeChat groups and Chinese-language social platforms (Weibo, Little Red Book) can fill a new restaurant in its first week — or keep a failing one empty indefinitely. Understanding how this community discovers and decides is foundational to restaurant marketing in this market.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: #333;">
          But Google Maps remains the dominant discovery channel even here — particularly for attracting customers from outside Markham's core community and for capturing the younger generation that grew up with Google rather than WeChat. A restaurant that wins Google AND community word-of-mouth is untouchable in this market.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section style="background: #f5f5f0; padding: 72px 24px;">
      <div style="max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <p style="text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; font-size: 0.78rem; color: #E85D04; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;">What We Do</p>
        <h2 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem); margin-bottom: 20px;">What We Do For Markham Restaurants</h2>
        <ul style="list-style: none; margin-top: 28px;">
          <li style="padding: 14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0d8; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;">
            <span style="color: #E85D04; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;">→</span>
            <span style="color: #333;"><strong>Google Maps Optimization for High-Competition Markets:</strong> Markham's restaurant Google competition is some of the toughest in the GTA. We do deep competitor analysis and build the specific signals needed to outperform established restaurants in your category.</span>
          </li>
          <li style="padding: 14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0d8; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;">
            <span style="color: #E85D04; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;">→</span>
            <span style="color: #333;"><strong>Multi-Platform Review Management:</strong> Markham's community cross-references Google with Yelp and Chinese-language platforms. We manage your reputation across every platform where your potential customers are forming opinions.</span>
          </li>
          <li style="padding: 14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0d8; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;">
            <span style="color: #E85D04; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;">→</span>
            <span style="color: #333;"><strong>Cross-GTA Visitor Capture:</strong> Markham draws food tourists from across Toronto and the GTA specifically for East Asian cuisine. We build content targeting these visiting customers who search "best dim sum Markham" or "authentic Sichuan GTA."</span>
          </li>
          <li style="padding: 14px 0; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;">
            <span style="color: #E85D04; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;">→</span>
            <span style="color: #333;"><strong>Social Content for Food-Sophisticated Audiences:</strong> Markham's dining community is exacting — they'll call out bad plating, incorrect technique, and inauthentic presentation. Our content strategy presents your restaurant's story accurately and compellingly to this audience.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section style="background: #f5f5f0; padding: 72px 24px;">
      <div style="max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <p style="text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; font-size: 0.78rem; color: #E85D04; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;">Also Serving</p>
        <h2 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem); margin-bottom: 24px;">Restaurant Marketing Across the GTA</h2>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 24px;">
          <a href="/locations/scarborough/" style="background: #fff; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500;">Scarborough</a>
          <a href="/locations/north-york/" style="background: #fff; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500;">North York</a>
          <a href="/locations/vaughan/" style="background: #fff; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500;">Vaughan</a>
          <a href="/locations/mississauga/" style="background: #fff; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500;">Mississauga</a>
          <a href="/locations/brampton/" style="background: #fff; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500;">Brampton</a>
          <a href="/locations/hamilton/" style="background: #fff; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500;">Hamilton</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section style="background: #E85D04; color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 80px 24px;">
      <div style="max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <h2 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem); color: #fff; margin-bottom: 28px;">
          Your Markham restaurant deserves to be found. Let's make it happen.
        </h2>
        <a href="/contact/" style="display: inline-block; background: #fff; color: #E85D04; padding: 16px 36px; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem;">Book a Free Google Audit</a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</BaseLayout>
